import warnings
warnings.simplefilter('ignore')
ps = range(0, 5)
qs = range(0, 5)
ds = range(1, 2)
parameters = product(ps, ds, qs)
parameters_list = list(parameters)
# ARMAbest_aic
results = []
best_aic = float("inf") # 
for param in parameters_list:
    try:
        #model = ARIMA(df_month.amount,order=(param[0], param[1], param[2])).fit()
        # SARIMAX ARIMA
        model = sm.tsa.statespace.SARIMAX(df_month.amount,
                                order=(param[0], param[1], param[2]),
                                #seasonal_order=(4, 1, 2, 12),
                                enforce_stationarity=False,
                                enforce_invertibility=False).fit()

    except ValueError:
        print(':', param)
        continue
    aic = model.aic
    if aic < best_aic:
        best_model = model
        best_aic = aic
        best_param = param
    results.append([param, model.aic])
# 
best_model.summary()

# future_monthdate_list
df_month2 = df_month[['amount']]
future_month = 4
last_month = pd.to_datetime(df_month2.index[len(df_month2)-1])
date_list = []
for i in range(future_month):
    # 
    year = last_month.year
    month = last_month.month
    """
    if month == 12:
        month = 1
        year = year+1
    else:
        month = month + 1
    """
    next_month_days = calendar.monthrange(year, month)[1]
    #print(next_month_days)
    last_month = last_month + timedelta(days=next_month_days)
    date_list.append(last_month)
print('date_list=', date_list)

# 3
future = pd.DataFrame(index=date_list, columns= df_month.columns)
df_month2 = pd.concat([df_month2, future])

# get_predictionpredicted_mean
df_month2['forecast'] = best_model.get_prediction(start=0, end=len(df_month2)).predicted_mean
# 
df_month2['forecast'][:2] =[None, None]
print(df_month2)

# 
plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif']=['SimHei'] #
plt.figure(figsize=(30,7))
df_month2.amount.plot(label='')
df_month2.forecast.plot(color='r', ls='--', label='')
plt.legend()
plt.title('')
plt.xlabel('')
plt.ylabel('')
plt.show()

                        '2010-01-24', '2010-02-07', '2011-01-08',

  'upper_window': 1,
})
